      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DAINTREE TOMMY (1) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when third (19.19) in a Grade 5 at this track. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. FREE SETTLER (8) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing third and beaten a nose (16.68) behind Rambling Aces at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Leading player again. ORLANDO BEACH (6) is worth forgiving last start after finishing sixth (20.24) from Box 4 at Capalaba over 366m. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from five starts. Likely to be thereabouts. FASCINATE MARK (7) is right in the mix.",
